      "value": "Learn the Comet spell."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered the <strong>Entropist</strong> Class. <br /></p></blockquote><p>You learn the ultimate <strong>Entropist</strong> spell: <strong>Comet</strong>. <br /></p><table style=\"width:94.2636%\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:12.973%\"></col><col style=\"width:13.1532%\"></col><col style=\"width:27.9279%\"></col><col style=\"width:45.7658%\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Comet</strong></td><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP: </strong>50</td><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target: </strong>Special</td><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration: </strong>Instantaneous</td></tr></tbody></table><p>You rip open a large portal to the Cosmos, calling down astral debris from the gaping void. Choose on option: one creature you can see suffers @DMG[60 untyped] damage; or you choose any number of creatures you can see, and each of them suffers @DMG[40 untyped] damage. These amounts increase by 5 if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, or by 10 if you are <strong>level 40 or higher</strong>.</p><p>Damage dealt by this spell has no type (thus being unaffected by damage Affinities).</p><hr /><p>Add the @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.spells.Item.Vem0KAbARyK1FtPk]{Comet} spell to your character sheet from the <strong>Entropist</strong> spell list.</p>",
